<ext_description linkend="Part_collection_mim.restrict_collection_category">
The <b>restrict_collection_category</b> rule constrains every instance of <b>product_definition</b> of type 'collection definition' to be a definition of a <b>product</b> of category 'collection'.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_collection_mim.restrict_collection_category.wr:WR1">
There shall not be any <b>product</b> referenced by the  attribute <b>of_product</b> of <b>product_definition_formation</b> that is not a 'collection'.
</ext_description>
